{"tid":783072,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"玩ocamp...比個組爸中出左...","createTime":"2018-08-17T09:30:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-05T17:35:28.000Z","uid":115982,"like":43,"dislike":674,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"e06f2f83abbdd6efe81bdaadca4845cdb41f2d8d","tid":783072,"uid":115982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T09:30:46.000Z","msg":"玩玩個房game啦，之後飲左好多...<br />\n我攤撚左...<br />\n之後迷迷糊糊feel到有個好照顧我既組爸扶左我去訓<br />\n其實我之前識佢嘅 打排球識架 <br />\n仲係咁問我有冇事使唔使同我睇醫生<br />\n最近同男朋友嗌交，佢呢三日都對我好好<br />\n我個下真係好開心有人咁樣關心我<br />\n夜晚玩完水戰campfire 件衫都仲未乾得透<br />\n佢扶左我入間房之後<br />\n我就覺得好凍好凍...佢幫我抹乾個我身先暖d<br />\n不過我著S碼 個心口都係紮實頂住頂住好緊...好唔舒服...<br />\n我迷迷糊糊之下除咗自己件衫 瞓咗係張床<br />\n呢一刻我覺得佢好似我男朋友咁。。。佢呢個時候捉住我隻手 我個下真係有少少忍唔住 於是就錫左落去...<br />\n<br />\n返到屋企訓醒 有d驚會有左bb，點算<br />\nPs. 男朋友係我屋企門口買左外賣tum我，我好亂呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68e4fdc762cdd29916c125c3033cab4157391ab4","tid":783072,"uid":25568,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T09:31:07.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"305fbd0118b8bda7fcefb3e06a22c37988aeb7f1","tid":783072,"uid":72454,"like":402,"dislike":6,"score":396,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T09:31:42.000Z","msg":"請善用起底功能"},{"pid":"99b842e8a974a5ed721bf8cf0f99ea5aba834b08","tid":783072,"uid":27745,"like":426,"dislike":3,"score":423,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T09:31:43.000Z","msg":"最後互射咗幾多次？"},{"pid":"600bffa5c21972a16f7a05966dab082a8eab15bd","tid":783072,"uid":182281,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T09:31:55.000Z","msg":"左入 定 右入？"},{"pid":"2dcf3571afe5ea4802b47e3e4a5f4368e8ee7d3b","tid":783072,"uid":188733,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T09:32:05.000Z","msg":"又一假膠"},{"pid":"29ee28908c05773b078515555e54f86cc94d3a78","tid":783072,"uid":42626,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T09:32:07.000Z","msg":"互射左幾多次？"},{"pid":